These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, 7up, tea, sprite, water
The people have 6 different hobbies: rock-climbing, collecting, dancing, camping, reading, sudoku
1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
7. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5     |    6    |
| Beverage   | water | almond-milk  | 7up    | tea  | hot-chocolate      | sprite    |
| Hobby      | collecting  | sudoku | reading | rock-climbing | camping | dancing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: western, spy, time-travel, comedy, epic, superhero
6 different pets are kept: chinchilla, snake, bird, horse, cat, fish
1. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
6. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
7. the person watching superhero movies is the owner of the fish##1
8. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
9. the person watching western movies is the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Movie-Genre   | western   | epic | spy | superhero | comedy     | time-travel  |
| Pet           | bird | snake    | chinchilla      | fish  | horse | cat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: electronic, funk, disco, gospel, salsa, trance
There are 6 different nationalities: russian, egyptian, turkish, thai, pakistani, canadian
1. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of trance##1
2. the thai is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
3. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
4. the fan of disco is on the right of the pakistani##1
5. the fan of salsa is on the right of the canadian##1
6. the fan of salsa is on the left of the egyptian##1
7. the thai is on the far right##1
8. the turkish is the fan of gospel##1
9. the fan of disco is the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel   | trance   | salsa      | funk | electronic  | disco   |
| Nationality   | turkish | canadian | russian | egyptian   | pakistani | thai |

