.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: salsa, pop, ambient, metal, d&b, reggae
The people use 6 different means of transport: train, scooter, bus, trike, quad-bike, boat
1. the person driving the train is on the far left##1
2. the fan of ambient is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
4. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
5. the person driving the boat is the fan of metal##1
6. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
7. the fan of d&b is on the far right##1
8. the person driving the bus is on the right of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |     3      |     4      |   5   |    6    |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | metal | salsa      | pop  | reggae | d&b |
| Transport     | train | boat  | quad-bike | bus | trike  | scooter    |

