.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-5::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: collecting, rock-climbing, writing, chess, puzzles, gardening
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: dubstep, reggae, pop, jazz, rock, funk
 1. the fan of pop is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
 3. the fan of rock is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 4. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
 5. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 6. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 7. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
 9. the fan of pop is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
10. the person who's hobby is chess is the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |
| Hobby         | chess | gardening | collecting | puzzles | rock-climbing | writing  |
| Music-Genre   | funk  | jazz  | pop  | dubstep | rock      | reggae |

