3. the malaysian is on the right of the fan of soul##1
4. the thai is on the left of the fan of punk##1
5. the russian is the fan of reggae##1
6. the fan of gospel is on the right of the pakistani##1
7. the canadian is on the far right##1
8. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
9. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | reggae    | funk    | punk | soul     | gospel   | techno     |
| Nationality   | russian | thai | argentine | pakistani | malaysian | canadian |

