3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the owner of the rat is the person driving the car##1
6. the owner of the mouse is the person driving the helicopter##1
7. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
8. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |   3   |     4      |   5   |     6      |
| Pet         | cat       | pony     | rat | mouse | rabbit | lizard |
| Transport   | van | bus | car | helicopter     | scooter  | tram       |

