2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the fan of dubstep##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
5. the person who's sport is handball is the fan of d&b##1
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
7. the fan of blues is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |     3      |     4      |   5   |       6       |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | blues  | folk     | techno    | indie  | dubstep          |
| Sport         | handball  | sailing | skateboarding | climbing | cricket | lacrosse |

