.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-9::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: coffee, water, fanta, lemonade, cola, almond-milk
The people use 6 different means of transport: trike, jet-ski, skateboard, scooter, roller, helicopter
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
8. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking water##1
9. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |    3     |   4    |       5       |     6      |
| Beverage    | cola | water | lemonade | almond-milk    | coffee | fanta      |
| Transport   | skateboard   | trike     | jet-ski      | roller | helicopter           | scooter |

