.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-10::.
There 6 different types of food: kale, strawberry, blueberry, radish, artichoke, garlic
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: crime, superhero, disaster, animation, romance, drama
1. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person eating kale is on the far right##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is the person eating strawberry##1
4. the person eating radish is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
5. the person watching animation movies is on the far right##1
6. the person eating strawberry is on the far left##1
7. the person eating garlic is the person watching crime movies##1
8. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
9. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |   5    |    6     |
| Food          | strawberry | garlic   | artichoke  | blueberry    | radish  | kale |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero   | crime | drama | romance | disaster | animation |

