.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-11::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk, milk, cola, sprite, hot-chocolate
The people have 6 different jobs:  engineer, accountant, entrepreneur, lawyer, videographer, dancer
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
