3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
4. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
6. the accountant is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking fanta is the lawyer##1
8. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
9. the videographer is on the left of the entrepreneur##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |   3   |      4      |    5     |     6     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate    | fanta     | milk | soy-milk | cola | sprite   |
| Job        | dancer | lawyer | videographer | entrepreneur   | engineer    | accountant |

