.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3     |       4       |       5       |    6     |
| Hobby   | photography | chess | cooking  | collecting | board-games       | drawing   |
| Sport   | golf | basketball     | sailing | cricket        | badminton | water-polo |

