.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-17::.
6 different pets are kept: pony, bird, chinchilla, mouse, ferret, lizard
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: volleyball, lacrosse, surfing, snowboarding, tennis, cricket
1. the owner of the ferret is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
