4. the owner of the mouse is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
6. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
8. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
9. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |    3     |    4     |    5    |       6       |
| Pet     | ferret  | mouse       | lizard   | pony      | chinchilla | bird          |
| Sport   | tennis | volleyball | surfing | lacrosse | snowboarding | cricket |

